    Have a Question?

    We are here to help!

    How do I use this scale?

    Using SmartEtek™ is straightforward: place food on the stainless-steel platform for instant measurement. 

    Connect to the VeSyncFit app for additional features, like nutrient tracking, customizing food data, and saving portion sizes. 

    You can also use the barcode scanner for quick and accurate logging. SmartEtek™ offers all you need for effective nutrition tracking.

    Is it compatible with my smartphone?

    SmartEtek™ is compatible with both iOS and Android devices. Simply download the free VeSyncFit app from the App Store or Google Play Store, and you're ready to go!

    How does the scale know what I'm putting on it?

    The SmartEtek™ scale works in conjunction with the VeSync app on your smartphone. 

    By connecting the scale to the app via Bluetooth, you can select the specific food item you're weighing from the extensive Nutritionix database within the app. 

    Once you've chosen the food item, simply place it on the scale, and the app communicates with the scale to accurately measure and display the nutritional information.

    How do I know if the scale isn't just showing random numbers about macros?

    Rest assured, SmartEtek™ Nutrition Food Scale provides accurate and reliable measurements. The scale's precision is ensured through its integration with the VeSync app, which cooperates with the Nutritionix database. 

    This database is the world's largest verified nutrition database, containing accurate information on a wide range of food items. 

    By connecting the scale to the app and selecting the food item you're weighing, you can trust that the displayed macros are based on verified nutritional data.

    Can multiple users track their nutrition using SmartEtek™?

    Absolutely! SmartEtek™ allows for multiple user profiles within the VeSyncFit app, making it ideal for families or households with multiple individuals. Each user can customize their profile and track their nutritional intake separately, ensuring personalized tracking for everyone.

    Is app free to use?

    Yes, the VeSync app is free to download and use.

    Is it easy to clean?

    Yes, SmartEtek™ is designed for convenience and ease of use. The premium food-grade stainless steel platform is durable and easy to wipe clean after each use. Simply use a damp cloth or sponge with mild detergent to clean the surface, ensuring your scale remains hygienic and ready for the next use.

    What do I do if I run into problems with my scale?

    No worries! If you have any issues with your SmartEtek™ scale, just remember that we offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. So, if you're not satisfied, you can always get your money back or exchange it for a new SmartEtek™ scale at no additional cost.
